name.ro: Save From Net Instagram Story - InstaStory

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Want to save your favorite Instagram stories, photos, videos, or reels? And want to view Instagram stories anonymously?

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
InstaStory is your perfect solution! ✨

InstaStory is a powerful Chrome extension that lets you easily download and view Instagram content.

Features:

1️⃣ Download any Instagram stories, photos, videos, or reels ⬇️
2️⃣ View Instagram stories anonymously
3️⃣ Simple interface is easy to use

With InstaStory, you can:
1️⃣ Save your favorite Instagram stories to your computer for offline viewing later
2️⃣ Share your favorite Instagram content with friends and family
View stories without worrying about being seen by the story owner

How to install:
1️⃣ Click "Add to Chrome"
2️⃣ Wait for the extension to install
3️⃣ Once installed, you can start using InstaStory!

Disclaimer:
InstaStory is not affiliated with Instagram or Facebook. It is a third-party developed Chrome extension. ⚠️

We are always working to improve InstaStory, if you have any feedback or suggestions, please feel free to contact us.
